CAROL:
I think I already know

20:27.727 --> 20:29.894
the answer to this,
but I got to ask.

20:29.896 --> 20:32.263
Can we bring Cher?

20:32.265 --> 20:33.831
No, right?

20:33.833 --> 20:35.066
Never mind. Delete.

